The paper deals with optical character recognition (OCR) in natural scene images, which is a problem in computer vision (CV). Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses recurrent neural networks (RNNs) and attention mechanisms, which are common in natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning (ML) research. Therefore, cs.CL, cs.LG, and cs.AI are also likely sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with text recognition, which is a problem in information retrieval (IR). Therefore, cs.IR is also a possible sub-category.
